frames.description: User opening Chrome browser, clicking on the Chrome icon in the dock
Typing 'gmail.com' in the address bar, using keyboard input
Pressing Enter to navigate to Gmail, page is loading
Gmail login page appears, user clicking on email input field
Typing email address 'user@company.com' in the login field
Clicking 'Next' button to proceed to password entry
Typing password in the password field (characters hidden)
Clicking 'Sign In' button to complete authentication
Gmail inbox loads, showing 23 unread emails in the inbox
Scrolling down through email list, scanning subject lines
Clicking on first email from 'Sarah Johnson' about 'Project Update'
Reading the email content, scrolling down to see full message
Clicking 'Reply' button at the bottom of the email
Typing reply message: 'Thanks for the update. When is the deadline?'
Clicking 'Send' button to send the reply
Navigating back to inbox by clicking 'Inbox' in left sidebar
Opening second email from 'Michael Chen' about 'Meeting Reschedule'
Reading the meeting reschedule request, checking proposed times
Switching to new tab by pressing Cmd+T to open calendar
Typing 'calendar.google.com' to check availability
Google Calendar loads, showing current week view
Clicking on Thursday 2 PM slot to check if it's available
Confirming the slot is free, switching back to Gmail tab
Clicking reply on Michael's email to confirm new meeting time
Typing reply: 'Thursday 2 PM works for me. I'll update my calendar.'
Sending the reply and returning to inbox view
Clicking on third email from 'IT Support' about 'System Maintenance'
Reading maintenance notification, noting it's scheduled for this weekend
Clicking 'Archive' button to move the informational email out of inbox
Scrolling down to see more emails in the inbox
Clicking on compose button to start a new email
Typing recipient email 'team@company.com' in the To field
Typing subject line 'Weekly Team Standup - Agenda Items'
Typing email body with agenda items and meeting details
Reviewing the composed email, checking for typos and completeness
Clicking 'Send' button to send the team agenda email
Email sent successfully, confirmation message appears
Closing Gmail tab and Chrome browser window
